Christian Bros Resolution Wants to Split News Corp. CEO, Chair

-- B y   W i l l   D a l e y
-- 
2011-10-18T13:33:04Z

-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2011-10-18/christian-bros-resolution-wants-to-split-news-corp-ceo-chair.html
Christian Brothers Investment
Services said it plans to introduce a floor resolution calling
for the separation of the chief executive officer and chair of
the board positions at  News Corp. (NWSA)  when the company holds its
annual shareholder meeting on Oct. 21 in  Los Angeles , according
to a statement.  To contact the editor responsible for this story:
Will Daley at 
 wdaley2@bloomberg.net  